_header: By Herodes day the king a priest was of good life
_description: The Expanded Nativity, a revision of a portion of 6380 — 897 long-line couplets

Bod779.First Lines:
Out of Sesar augostus þer com a soche
                    lymÞat was fram þe emperour þat hyȝt
                    octauyan…
Bod779.Last Lines:
…& þus endeþ þe gospel amyd winter
                    nyȝtnow crist vs sende helpe of soule þat al may dele &
                    dyȝt

BLEge1993.First Lines:
Bi eroudes day þe king a prest was of god lifþat Zakarie
                    was ihote and elisabeþ is wif…
BLEge1993.Last Lines:
…Phelip hedde al iturie heroudes galileAnd lisanie abiline and
                    pilatus Iude
